Privacy Policy for AI Guardian Web Shield

AI Guardian Web Shield is designed with a privacy-first approach. The extension analyzes webpage links and content locally within the user's browser in order to identify potential phishing indicators, suspicious language patterns, and other possible security risks.

Data Collection
AI Guardian Web Shield does not collect personally identifiable information. The extension processes webpage content locally on the user's device and does not transmit browsing data to external servers.

Data Storage
The extension may store user preferences locally within the browser using Chrome storage APIs. This may include interface settings and protection configuration choices. No personal data is stored.

Data Sharing
AI Guardian Web Shield does not sell, transfer, or share personal data with third parties.

Remote Code
AI Guardian Web Shield does not use remote code execution. All analysis scripts are packaged within the extension.

Purpose
The sole purpose of the extension is to provide plain-language guidance about potential security risks in webpages and links in order to help users make informed browsing decisions.

